o
ut and put a fresh roller in, you see, and then they ran backwards and forwards between this, er, frame each end, the rollers did. Um, then they come out, um, there's a biggish table mother used to work on. You, er, you just put the rollers, and, er, hand
 
folded the things. Then the things had to be folded round another roller, you see, the things to be ironed. (Well of course) they're folded properly, had to be folded round and, well, 'course, sheets would have to be done separately, couldn't put a lot of
