\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 No, us children just went. Father didn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Did your mother have any social outings and any activities outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Er, can't say that she did.
