\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Er, yes, er, used to, \{BLANK\} she used to take me the little (..) \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 church, when I was early, early on, you see, in the afternoon, Sunday afternoon.
