\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Were you on good terms with the policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Were your family on good terms with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 You weren't brought up to say, your mother say "I'll call a policeman" and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Oh, no, no. One policeman, he h
ad a large family, one of the older policemen, and, er, he used to wait for them to come home from school (..) late with a shake or a belt each month, you know. I believe there's some of that same family in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Chelmsford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} now. \{ILLEGIBLE\} Inspector Pertt \{BLANK\} they're probably retired, now, and, er, then we had \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 and, er, big moustache, and he was very, um, reserved and very quiet. He wouldn't give himself away at all, no, not with the farmers and dealers, you know, very strict attention to his duti
es, and then the other one was, er, Cole, as I said, P.C.Cole, and, er, oh, yes, we were on good terms with them. When I was in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Mesopotamia{\*\xmlclose}
, Mrs. Cole, I remember, made me mince pies, sent me a parcel out. It used to take four months, you see, by the time I got a letter or parcel, and then there was return letter, er, (..) \{BLANK\}
 long time, and some walnuts, they sent out, they got, er, they'd got little roots, you can imagine the, er, temperature, temperature out there was..
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Encouraged them to grow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Yes. So there may be some walnut trees in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Persia
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Mesopotamia{\*\xmlclose} that originated from here, from (..)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 And in the village, the Tritton family were so very good to you, weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Oh, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Was there in the village a strong feeling of community, with everybody belonging to something together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 
Mm. Yes, I think so. They had an annual show, you know, a, um, more-or-less a, a flower show they used to call it, and, er, earlier on at, the school, the, the gardener would bring, er
, gera-, geranium cuttings, little pots with cuttings in, and then at the annual show the one or the, um, would get a prize with the best, best geranium er, plant, you know, developed from those cuttings (..) and, they were liberals really, the, the Tritt
ons, not Conservative, and, er, they didn't mix up, you know, there was no, er, no mixing up with, er, politics with the village life, not..
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 You mean, they didn't discriminate against a person because their family was Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Oh, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 And your family was Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Yes, really, really, yes. Er, I think I mentioned in, er, in the little notes about, er, (..)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Oh, that's your medal, oh yes, I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 I think I mentioned that, when, er, when they had..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 It's a nicely done thing, isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11482670 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 It's nicely made. (..) \{BLANK\} Majority 2,545.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8668315 HT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11813394\charrsid8658109 Yes.
